         <h3>10 tips for healthy living</h3>
         <!--<h5>Delicious, Nutritious, Super-fast food</h5>-->
        
         <p>Eating healthily doesn't mean eating boring food  quite the opposite, in fact. The key to a healthy diet is a varied, balanced diet. So that means eating lots of different, delicious things. It's fine to have a burger for dinner or a slice of cake on a Sunday afternoon if it's part of a healthy diet and active lifestyle. To help you get the balance right, here's Jamie's top 10 tips to make sure you eat well and feel happy.<br />
<br />
And remember, we all deserve a treat sometimes.</p>
       
